code: function generateId(length){var chars='0123456789ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXTZabcdefghiklmnopqrstuvwxyz'.split('');if(!length){length=Math.floor(Math.random()*chars.length);}var str='';for(var i=0;i<length;i++){str+=chars[Math.floor(Math.random()*chars.length)];}return str;}export default generateId;export{generateId};
